{"tid":1887314,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[有圖] 林鄭同班官去派口罩物資嘅地方，基本上都係藍區","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T08:43:25.000Z","uid":7439,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"19d506bba36bda719b2a09f10390a2e1afba4dad","tid":1887314,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfTx2rd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfTx2rd.jpg&h=b90ff4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺地圖圈個大概位置出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>林鄭月娥 藍田德田邨</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/17/P2020021700792_photo_1171407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F17%2FP2020021700792_photo_1171407.jpg&h=95d959e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><strong>廣德 J17</strong><br />\n廣田邨、德田邨（德義樓、德樂樓、德欣樓、德康樓、德盛樓、德隆樓）及康盈苑<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯 ①. 柯創盛 4,514 51.06% </span><br />\n人民力量 ②. 譚得志 4,327 48.94%</blockquote><br />\n林鄭藍田德田邨派口罩，會喺柯創盛(民建聯)定葉梓傑(民主黨)嘅選區派？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1884570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1884570</a><br />\n<br />\n柯創盛今年就連任硬立法會㗎啦，係睇會留喺九龍東定係去超區留個位比佐敦谷嘅顔汶羽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>林鄭月娥 九龍城新益樓「樂屋」(恒基撥予樂善堂的「社會房屋」)及鄰近劏房</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/17/P2020021700792_photo_1171413.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F17%2FP2020021700792_photo_1171413.jpg&h=06e84351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>龍城 G11<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">民建聯 ①. 吳寶強 1,983 49.97%</span><br />\n無黨派 ②. 方毅妍 101 2.55%<br />\n民主派區選聯盟 ③. 馮達浚 1,884 47.48%</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n99票險勝，成功第三次連任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>鄭若驊 元朗朗善邨(聯同博愛醫院)</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/18/P2020021800612_photo_1171418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F18%2FP2020021800612_photo_1171418.jpg&h=22dd2dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>十八鄉東 M11<br />\n鄉事派 ①. 林添福 1,500 39.21% <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民主動力 ②. 李俊威 1,838 48.04% </span><br />\n鄉事派 ③. 黃柏仁 488 12.75%</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十八鄉今屆三拆四，但結果死剩沈豪杰，但三席係有兩席多得鄉事派攬炒，包括呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>楊潤雄 荃灣福來邨(聯同仁濟醫院主席王賢訊)</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2565000/2567941/86864316_2289117181387804_8328702569249505280_o_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2565000%2F2567941%2F86864316_2289117181387804_8328702569249505280_o_1024.jpg&h=c200b7bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>福來 K05<br />\n獨立 ①. 伍嘉儀 226 4.15%<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">工聯會 ②. 葛兆源 2,871 52.70%</span><br />\n民主黨 ③. 黃湛聯 2,351 43.15%</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n荃灣一點藍，佢老婆所謂「小花」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />劉桂容可能仲出名過佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>楊偉雄 屯門綠苑(新鴻基交予仁愛堂營運的「過渡性社會房屋」)</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2565000/2567941/87054349_2541647786057929_3173553345059094528_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2565000%2F2567941%2F87054349_2541647786057929_3173553345059094528_n_1024.jpg&h=cff90f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>寶田 L25<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">實政圓桌 ①. 蘇嘉雯 2,562 57.61%</span><br />\n屯門十兄弟 ②. 張贊華 1,885 42.39% </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實政圓桌兩個死剩種其中之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>羅致光 大角嘴(聯同東華三院)</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/17/P2020021700792_photo_1171402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F17%2FP2020021700792_photo_1171402.jpg&h=dd39578c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東華三院賽馬會大角咀綜合服務中心(通州街28號頌賢花園)<br />\n<blockquote>大南 E13<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">社區前進 ①. 李國權 2,943 58.32%</span><br />\n無黨派 ②. 蔡其隆 57 1.13%<br />\n經民聯 ③. 李思敏 2,046 40.55%</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>劉江華 旺角(聯同旺角街坊會)</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202002/17/P2020021700792_photo_1171404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F17%2FP2020021700792_photo_1171404.jpg&h=1b565e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角街坊會(大角咀福全街45號)<br />\n<blockquote>大角咀南 E10<br />\n民建聯 ①. 蔡少峰 2,068 44.00%<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民主黨 ②. 曾自鳴 2,632 56.00%</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角大角咀冇指明係邊度<br />\n靠估啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上面係純粹跟個竇口嘅位置<br />\n<br />\n大南35年來第一次翻盤，嗰度最出名嘅可能係鮮魚行學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角街坊會位置極度接近油尖旺三個死剩種其中兩個<span style=\"color: blue;\">許德亮(旺角西E06)、鍾澤暉(櫻桃E09)</span><br />\n可能係派去嗰度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9d18cd2e3b724253e306a5479670e11c007ffd","tid":1887314,"uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭去嘅觀塘同九龍城，就係今屆少數派最頑強最紅嘅兩區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CC8Rdnu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCC8Rdnu.png&h=8f56d65e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df7a51bba5dd2a0549406141f2b18e23a982fe0f","tid":1887314,"uid":9603,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-